title: OCE Open Ladder D3+ Top Lane & Jungle Required
body:
As title looking for a D3+ Top Lane and Jungler for Open Ladder, if you are interested please add me and we can talk further.

If you are unable to attend all Qualifiers listed on the Open Ladder Page no need to inquire.

replies.body: I'm silver 4 and would like to try out for top lane I've been told many times I don't belong in low elo. To show my intrest I think if I gained a try out I'll be quick to only impress you. IGN 4 7
